{"tid":605841,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》片長2小時36分鐘，成Marvel有史以來最長的電影","createTime":"2018-03-26T04:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T08:37:29.000Z","uid":178284,"like":38,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"cd85cca3b3c3460510c38c2213fc8126ea6de858","tid":605841,"uid":178284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-IZA-PR1kcIc/Wrh1blaBoqI/AAAAAAAAABU/sSqyM9xSRlIWjDHzbw3MNbph8v93A8KLACLcBGAs/s1600/Avengers-Infinity-War-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-IZA-PR1kcIc%2FWrh1blaBoqI%2FAAAAAAAAABU%2FsSqyM9xSRlIWjDHzbw3MNbph8v93A8KLACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FAvengers-Infinity-War-poster.jpg&h=ddf2a46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》已經快上映了，它是跨越10年的第18部Marvel電影。今次相當多超級英雄出場， 《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》將會是漫威有史以來最長的電影，但擊敗了以前的記錄持有者《美國隊長3：內戰》。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國票務網站Fandango，這部電影將長156分鐘(兩小時36分鐘)。這比《美國隊長3：內戰》時間長9分鐘，並擊敗了前兩部復仇者電影：《復仇者聯盟》歷時2小時23分鐘，而《復仇者聯盟2：奧創紀元》長2小時21分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n最近，俄羅斯兄弟公司談到哪個角色的出場時間最多：&ldquo;Thanos在這部電影中擁有令人難以置信的出場時間，在很多方面我都會說這是Thanos的電影。&rdquo;同時，《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》的最新預告片已成為24小時內第三大最多人觀看的預告片 - 而紀錄保持者仍然是第一部《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》預告片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4a258daffd16b6e7a339ea567bd403684a6284","tid":605841,"uid":176304,"like":0,"dislike":42,"score":-42,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:26:36.000Z","msg":"MARVEL 外 最長係咪亞凡達定鐵達尼???"},{"pid":"4414ea7446b78ca0b7cf730a6a6da13b67ef233b","tid":605841,"uid":68598,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"cd4a258daffd16b6e7a339ea567bd403684a6284","tid":605841,"uid":176304,"like":0,"dislike":42,"score":-42,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:26:36.000Z","msg":"MARVEL 外 最長係咪亞凡達定鐵達尼???"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:27:44.000Z","msg":"titanic 3個鐘15分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=